chunks.text: Sarah: Let's discuss the Q4 roadmap. We need to finalize the pricing strategy. Mike: I think we should go with the tiered pricing model we discussed. Sarah: Agreed. The enterprise tier at $99/month seems reasonable.

Mike: We also need to circle back on the Redis configuration for caching. Sarah: Right, remind me to review the deployment scripts before we launch. Mike: Action item: I'll sync with Lisa on the marketing copy by Wednesday.
